have been earmarked by conservative instinct yet openmindedness 
theres no ideological fervor 
but liberals expressed some wariness 
were looking at the nomination very cautiously said susan 
liss legal director for people for the american way 
i think the most interesting thing about starrs selection is 
that it gives the administration another seat in the dc circuit to 
fill she said starr has been a less reliable conservative than 
