now an artist in poway calif 
buchers letter appeared in proceedings and naval history 
magazines published by the us naval institute in annapolis a 
professional society for sea services personnel 
to mark the 20th anniversary of the pueblo incident the 1988 
fall issue of naval history published the reflections of five flag 
officers who were involved in the incident 
