paul stillwell editorinchief of naval history 
i was surprised when i saw the initial article ninety 
percent of what was in that article was never mentioned during the 
pueblo inquiry it was filled with misinformation bucher said 
the pueblo lacked the proper equipment to repel an attack navy 
