where water is up to the first deck and is heeled over 25 degrees 
two argentine vessels were headed to the vessel to try to pump 
the remaining fuel from the ship and salvage it if possible but it 
remained in danger of sinking and had drifted against a nearby 
island he said 
in argentina the government news agency telam reported that the 
