canadas yukon will plunge southward warned weather service 
meteorologist john jannuzzi in seattle 
no deaths or injuries directly attributable to the cold had been 
reported in alaska there has been speculation by the governor and 
others that icy fog may have contributed to sundays crash of a 
canadian military plane that killed eight men 
