durn just when you write off the whole danged 
network season cbs comes along with a big ol event a fournight 
masterpiece of a western lonesome dove 
the eighthour miniseries begins sunday and runs through 
wednesday 
readers who loved larry mcmurtrys pulitzer prizewinning novel 
