more quickly than the book by the end of the first night the trail 
drive is under way and the first fatality has occurred at the nueces 
river by then any viewer with a pulse should be hooked 
in exchange for the quicker pace the miniseries shucks some of 
the character development of the book theres no way around that 
unless the network stretched the miniseries into a week after four 
nights viewers might wish that they had 
