merchandise wholesaler 
the document an estimate of the commissions owed was intended 
for k mart headquarters in troy mich k mart is appealing the 
judgment 
it is a danger agrees king its like mail without an 
envelope and you can make a lot of mistakes 
just like the us postal service junk mail is a problem 
